title: EP.38: NEW PRO BOWL, OTA'S, WARRIORS VS CELTICS, TEAM A OR TEAM B, AND MUCH MORE!
description: In this episode we go over what the NFL could do to make the pro bowl more interesting, we talk about the warriors in the finals, the strange OTA rules, and we come up with teams we need you to choose between, along with a lot more random stuff. TUNE IN!!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
